## Why Only **Create**?

Instead of generating a full CRUD garden, the initializer provides a **minimal Create use case**:

* Keeps the scaffold **lean and comprehensible**.
* Shows the full flow across **all hexagonal layers**.
* Leaves room for you to extend with Update/Delete/Search as exercises.

